  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to provide an investigational drug to patients with a specific
      type of hypercholesterolemia (high cholesterol) or sitosterolemia (unusually high absorption
      of non-cholesterol sterols) in a treatment use setting.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
